al-Aflādh al-zabarjadīyah fī madāʼiḥ al-ʻiṭrah al-ṭāhirah al-Aḥmadīyah
ḥilyat al-ʻaṣr al-jadīd fī shamāʼil al-malik al-ḥamīd
Muḍāḥāt amthāl Kitāb Kalīlah wa-Dimnah bi-mā ashbahahu min ashʻār al-ʻArab
Marātiʻ al-ghizlān fī waṣf al-ḥisān min al-ghilmān
Sāniḥāt dumá al-qaṣr fī muṭāraḥāt banī al-ʻaṣr
Sirāj kull sārin li-sīrat al-wārith lil-mukhtār
